1
00:01:10,080 --> 00:01:11,600
Ms. Situ, Mr. Du.

2
00:01:12,600 --> 00:01:14,800
Let me start by apologizing to you both.

3
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:17,180
Since you arrived in Dayang Village,

4
00:01:17,240 --> 00:01:20,360
I haven't even treated you to a decent meal.

5
00:01:21,320 --> 00:01:22,800
I've really been too busy.

6
00:01:23,039 --> 00:01:24,600
I happen to have time today,

7
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:26,320
so I insisted on inviting you two

8
00:01:26,320 --> 00:01:27,640
to my humble home for a meal.

9
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:28,880
Let's have a drink.

10
00:01:28,960 --> 00:01:30,690
I'll drink first as an apology.

11
00:01:31,440 --> 00:01:33,759
Boss Xiao, you're being so polite today.

12
00:01:35,360 --> 00:01:36,690
What do you want from us?

13
00:01:39,360 --> 00:01:40,479
Since Mr. Du asked,

14
00:01:40,479 --> 00:01:41,800
I'll be direct.

15
00:01:41,880 --> 00:01:44,160
I know you two have been investigating me.

16
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:45,960
I really want to tell you to stop.

17
00:01:46,320 --> 00:01:47,720
Aside from wasting time,

18
00:01:48,039 --> 00:01:48,970
it's pointless.

19
00:01:49,240 --> 00:01:52,039
I really haven't done anything bad.

20
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:54,840
Really?

21
00:02:00,080 --> 00:02:02,520
Are you testing us, Boss Xiao?

22
00:02:03,240 --> 00:02:04,240
Absolutely not.

23
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:06,880
I invited you here today

24
00:02:06,880 --> 00:02:07,960
because I really,

25
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:10,960
sincerely want to be friends with you both.

26
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:13,600
Don't be so fake with us here.

27
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:16,560
We know exactly what you're made of.

28
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:18,560
Just speak your mind.

29
00:02:19,320 --> 00:02:20,360
Since Mr. Du insists,

30
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:22,480
I'll get straight to the point.

31
00:02:24,160 --> 00:02:24,960
Ms. Situ.

32
00:02:25,160 --> 00:02:27,400
We are all businessmen.

33
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:29,250
And businessmen chase profit.

34
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:31,760
Now, regarding the restructuring of this mine,

35
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:32,640
in this matter,

36
00:02:32,720 --> 00:02:34,400
we've invested so much manpower and resources,

37
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:35,960
but no one is making money.

38
00:02:36,079 --> 00:02:37,880
No one is getting any benefit.

39
00:02:38,040 --> 00:02:42,160
If you ask me, we should reach a settlement.

40
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:45,579
I'd like to hear what kind of settlement.

41
00:02:47,760 --> 00:02:48,560
What I...

42
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:51,079
mean is this.

43
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:54,240
I hope you can give me another six months.

44
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:55,200
In six months,

45
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:57,460
I will hand over the mine to you smoothly.

46
00:02:57,640 --> 00:02:59,360
Not only will I hand it over,

47
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:02,880
I will divide all the revenue from these six months into three shares,

48
00:03:02,880 --> 00:03:05,080
and distribute them equally to you two.

49
00:03:05,640 --> 00:03:06,480
Xiao Tianman.

50
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:09,760
Do you know you are openly offering a bribe?

51
00:03:10,880 --> 00:03:12,320
What if I refuse?

52
00:03:16,440 --> 00:03:17,560
If you refuse,

53
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:19,640
then it will be a fight to the death.

54
00:03:19,640 --> 00:03:20,400
Won't it?

55
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,079
Of course,

56
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:24,560
that's not the outcome I want to see.

57
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:27,400
Besides,

58
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:28,930
your Shanshui Group

59
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:30,880
isn't desperate for a mine like this.

60
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:32,720
You have so many mines, right?

61
00:03:32,720 --> 00:03:34,360
There is no need, in such a small place,

62
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:36,360
for us to be at each other's throats.

63
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:39,160
I sincerely hope

64
00:03:39,160 --> 00:03:42,120
you two can put aside your prejudice against me

65
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:44,000
and accept me as a friend.

66
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:45,760
A friend?

67
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:49,050
Be friends with you?

68
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:50,400
Xiao Tianman,

69
00:03:51,480 --> 00:03:53,480
you have so many charges against you.

70
00:03:53,480 --> 00:03:54,440
Loan sharking,

71
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:57,480
illegal mining, organized crime, and murder.

72
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:59,930
How would I dare to be friends with you?

73
00:04:01,880 --> 00:04:02,720
Ms. Situ,

74
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:05,970
you shouldn't joke about some things.

75
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:09,360
You need proof when you speak.

76
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,650
I have just one thing to say.

77
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:15,080
God is always watching.

78
00:04:15,600 --> 00:04:18,200
Xiao Tianman, just wait for your retribution.

79
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:19,850
I also have one thing to say.

80
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:22,480
I have a clear conscience.

81
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,160
I'm not afraid of retribution.

82
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:26,960
Xiao Tianman, you really have no shame.

83
00:04:27,440 --> 00:04:28,520
What did you say?

84
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:29,600
What?

85
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:31,080
You want another murder on your record?

86
00:04:31,080 --> 00:04:33,400
All right. We'll skip the meal.

87
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:36,240
Xiao Tianman, your era is over.

88
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:39,440
You're just counting down the days now. You can't escape.

89
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:41,880
I suggest you keep your nose clean.

90
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:44,980
Maybe you can plead for a suspended death sentence.

91
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:47,300
I won't see you out.

92
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:54,159
What are you doing?

93
00:04:54,159 --> 00:04:54,960
Sit down.

94
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:57,240
Eat the food.

95
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:58,100
Don't waste it.

96
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:10,000
Xiao Li found something.

97
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:12,320
Preliminary investigation identifies them as Jiang Xiaomei's parents.

98
00:05:12,320 --> 00:05:14,080
Judging by the decomposition,

99
00:05:14,320 --> 00:05:16,580
they must have been buried on a rainy day.

100
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:19,420
It was likely done by Xiao Tianman's men.

101
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:22,700
Do we have solid evidence?

102
00:05:24,440 --> 00:05:25,280
Not yet.

103
00:05:27,280 --> 00:05:29,960
But we can make him think we do.

104
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:45,120
Mr. Xiao, what brings you here?

105
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:50,080
I heard two bodies were found in the village,

106
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:51,340
so I came to take a look.

107
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:54,040
Have the bodies been identified?

108
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:58,040
Yes. It's Uncle and Aunt Jiang.

109
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:01,720
Didn't you tell me

110
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:03,180
that they went out of town?

111
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:04,400
Yes.

112
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:07,520
I also heard from others that they went out of town.

113
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:11,520
This has something to do with you, doesn't it?

114
00:06:11,520 --> 00:06:12,760
Ms. Situ Hongtang,

115
00:06:13,400 --> 00:06:14,200
I know

116
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:16,680
you have a problem with me,

117
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:19,000
but you can't just pin this on me.

118
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:21,120
You need hard evidence.

119
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:25,400
I have an eyewitness.

120
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:31,480
I said I have an eyewitness.

121
00:06:36,520 --> 00:06:39,050
It was raining heavily that night, wasn't it?

122
00:06:45,960 --> 00:06:46,760
Wait,

123
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:49,800
what does the rain have to do with me?

124
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:52,800
Mr. Xiao, we have a meeting.

125
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,380
We're going to be late.

126
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,480
Don't push it.

127
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:37,480
Look at me.

128
00:07:41,280 --> 00:07:45,240
Who exactly saw it that night?

129
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:47,600
Mr. Xiao.

130
00:07:48,159 --> 00:07:49,820
There was really no one there.

131
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,760
You know me.

132
00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:53,740
I'm always careful in my work.

133
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:55,500
The tasks you assigned me,

134
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:57,040
I handled them flawlessly.

135
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:58,840
There have never been any slip-ups.

136
00:07:58,840 --> 00:08:00,320
I really don't know this time.

137
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:01,250
I don't know why.

138
00:08:01,320 --> 00:08:02,480
I don't know why this happened.

139
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,610
I really don't know.

140
00:08:03,760 --> 00:08:04,690
Don't be afraid.

141
00:08:07,840 --> 00:08:08,900
Then let me ask you.

142
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:12,280
Why did Situ Hongtang mention a witness?

143
00:08:13,880 --> 00:08:15,940
Why did she know it rained that night?

144
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:17,480
Why?

145
00:08:18,280 --> 00:08:19,540
I don't know, Mr. Xiao.

146
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:20,730
I really don't know.

147
00:08:21,080 --> 00:08:23,280
You must believe me.

148
00:08:30,960 --> 00:08:31,440
Investigate.

149
00:08:31,440 --> 00:08:32,169
Understood.

150
00:08:36,679 --> 00:08:38,140
Investigate thoroughly.

151
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:42,799
Find out exactly how much Situ Hongtang knows.

152
00:08:45,040 --> 00:08:46,240
Don't screw up again.

153
00:09:42,880 --> 00:09:44,760
Bro. We...

154
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,200
Why did you come back?

155
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:50,200
What for?

156
00:09:50,520 --> 00:09:52,360
We came to help you mine. Yeah.

157
00:09:52,520 --> 00:09:54,450
Do you think what I say is bullshit?

158
00:09:54,520 --> 00:09:56,360
Three people earn money faster than one, right?

159
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:58,160
We just want to keep you company.

160
00:09:58,480 --> 00:09:59,520
That's not what you said this afternoon.

161
00:09:59,520 --> 00:10:01,600
This afternoon, you said you wanted to mine more.

162
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:03,440
I... I... Someone is coming.

163
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:18,360
Xie Lao'er.

164
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,680
Who is he carrying?

165
00:10:23,040 --> 00:10:23,840
I don't know.

166
00:10:24,400 --> 00:10:25,800
Should we call the police?

167
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:28,280
Call the police for what? We would be exposed.

168
00:10:28,280 --> 00:10:29,880
I don't want to get involved in their families' business.

169
00:10:29,880 --> 00:10:31,200
That's a human life.

170
00:10:32,640 --> 00:10:34,770
Alright, alright. I'll go take a look.

171
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:58,960
Wake up.

172
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:00,920
Wake up.
